{{Multiple issues|{{notability|1=Events|date=June 2018}}{{primary sources|date=June 2018}}}}
The '''GreenTec Awards''' are an international [[environmental award]] based in [[Germany]]. Founded in 2008 by the Berlin-based consultancy VKP engineering GmbH, the prize honors projects, products, and people contributing to the protection of the environment.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.greentec-awards.com/en|title=GreenTec Awards - Internationaler Umweltpreis|last=Awards|first=Greentec|date=|website=www.greentec-awards.com|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vkpartner.de|title=VKPartner|website=www.vkpartner.de|language=de|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref> The GreenTec Awards were formerly known as the Clean Tech Media Awards.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.heise.de/tp/features/Streit-um-GreenTec-Awards-3399398.html|title=Streit um GreenTec Awards|last=Mühlbauer|first=Peter|website=Telepolis|language=de-DE|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref>
In 2017, [[Canada]] was the partner country of the GreenTec Awards;<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.canadainternational.gc.ca/germany-allemagne/media/GreenTec_Canada_Top10.aspx?lang=eng|title=Canada is Partner Country of GreenTec Awards 2017 – 10 Canadian Companies Nominated for TOP 10 in different categories|last=Government of Canada|first=Foreign Affairs Trade and Development Canada|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref> [[Norway]] is official partner for 2019.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessportal-norwegen.com/2018/05/14/norwegen-wird-gastland-des-greentec-awards-2019/|title=Norwegen wird Partnerland der GreenTec Awards 2019|last=businessportalnorwegen|date=2018-05-14|work=BusinessPortal Norwegen|access-date=2018-06-01|language=de-DE}}</ref> In 2018, the GreenTec Awards opened the IFAT, the world's biggest trade fair for environmental technologies, for the third time.<ref name="GreenTec Awards prior to IFAT">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ifat.de/trade-fair/supporting-program/greentec-awards/index.html|title=GreenTec Awards prior to IFAT|website=www.ifat.de|language=en|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://recyclinginternational.com/gallery/greentec-awards/|title=Greentec Awards • Recycling International|date=2018-05-17|work=Recycling International|access-date=2018-06-01|language=en-US}}</ref>
== Contest == The GreenTec Awards are awarded annually in varying categories. Additionally, there are "Special Prizes".{{Citation needed|date=June 2018}}
=== Certification === The competition of the GreenTec Awards is supervised by [[TÜV NORD|TÜV Nord]] in order to ensure fairness and transparency in the selection of the laureates.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tuev-nord-group.com/en/newsroom/press-releases/details/article/tuev-nord-tests-transparent-selection-process-of-the-greentec-awards/|title=TÜV NORD tests transparent selection process of the "GreenTec Awards"|date=2018-04-18|website=www.tuev-nord-group.com|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref> The award process received the certificate "Certified process of competition" by TÜV Nord.<ref name=":0" />
=== Jury === Currently, a 75-member jury with independent representatives from business, media, and science choses two of the three finalists per category – the third finalist is determined via a public online voting.<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.wallstreet-online.de/nachricht/9118578-iq-power-licensing-ag-among-the-top-10-for-the-greentec-awards-2017|title=Among the TOP 10 for the GreenTec Awards 2017|date=2016-11-24|work=wallstreet-online.de|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref> In an annual jury meeting, the top 3 projects are presented and discussed and the winners are chosen in a secret vote.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.gettyimages.co.uk/event/greentec-awards-jury-meeting-2015-539952619#/franziska-knuppe-attends-the-greentec-awards-jury-meeting-2015-at-picture-id464359280|title=GreenTec Awards Jury Meeting 2015|work=Getty Images|access-date=2018-06-01|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://industry24h.com/greentec-awards-finalists-confirmed/|title=GreenTec Awards finalists have been confirmed • INDUSTRY24h|website=industry24h.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref>
== Award ceremony == The GreenTec Awards are awarded at an annual gala event with 1000 guests from business and industry, science, politics, media, and showbiz.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bild.de/regional/muenchen/awards/greentec-award-2018-55685856.bild.html|title=GreenTec Awards 2018 - Minister und Motorsportler auf grüner Mission|work=bild.de|access-date=2018-06-01|language=de}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=GreenTec Awards|title=GreenTec Awards 2018|date=2018-05-22|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hDgFwyOf-gg|accessdate=2018-06-01}}</ref> The event alternately takes place in [[Berlin]] and [[Munich]] and is organized in collaboration with partners from different social sectors, such as [[Fraunhofer Society|Fraunhofer]], [[WILO group|Wilo]], and the [[German Association of the Automotive Industry|Germany Association of the Automotive Industry]] (VDA).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/WiloGroup/photos/a.518374288201340.1073741827.152125264826246/698584330180334/|title=WILO SE|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://corporate.wilo-dev.com/watermanagement/ifat-2016-alt/greentec-awards/#.WxFOzC_5xBw|title=Water Management - GreenTec Awards - WILO|website=corporate.wilo-dev.com|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iosb.fraunhofer.de/servlet/is/Entry.68784.Display/|title=blackValue bei den GreenTec Awards 2017|website=www.iosb.fraunhofer.de|language=de|access-date=2018-06-01}}</ref><ref name=":2" /> With music acts, media partners like [[Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung]], [[Wirtschaftswoche|WirtschaftsWoche]] and [[ProSieben]], and a "Green Carpet", the GreenTec Awards seek to make the topic of environmental protection more appealing to the broad public.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.gettyimages.co.uk/event/greentec-awards-2018-775162363#model-christina-attends-the-greentec-awards-2018-at-icm-munich-on-may-picture-id958219326|title=GreenTec Awards 2018|work=Getty Images|access-date=2018-06-01|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.gala.de/beauty-fashion/fashion/greentec-awards--tops---flops-vom-gruenen-teppich-21365896.html|title=GreenTec Awards: Tops + Flops vom grünen Teppich|date=2017-05-13|work=GALA|access-date=2018-06-01|language=de-DE}}</ref>
