{{expand language|topic=|langcode=AR|otherarticle=قبيلة كبدانة|date=March 2017}}'''Kebdana''' is a [[Riffian people|Riffian]] tribe of [[Berber/Arabic people|Berber]] origin that lives in the [[Rif]] mountainous region of northern [[Morocco]], at east of the city of [[Nador]] and at west of the city of [[Berkane]].
